386
00:16:55,360 --> 00:16:56,159
Bien.

387
00:16:56,240 --> 00:16:57,480
No importa lo malo que sea

388
00:16:57,480 --> 00:16:58,279
tu mano es,

389
00:16:58,360 --> 00:16:59,919
