403
00:17:22,279 --> 00:17:22,759
Ocho círculos.
Gano yo.

404
00:17:24,240 --> 00:17:25,440
Yo también.

405
00:17:25,480 --> 00:17:26,519
Y yo.

406
00:17:27,000 --> 00:17:28,720
Una ficha, tres ganadores.

407
00:17:28,960 --> 00:17:29,720
Sr. Zhu,

408
00:17:30,519 --> 00:17:31,440
