499
00:23:04,960 --> 00:23:05,359
Aquí.

500
00:23:29,720 --> 00:23:30,599
Es un poco pequeño.

501
00:23:32,680 --> 00:23:33,319
Das la talla.

502
00:23:52,440 --> 00:23:53,640
