532
00:27:43,880 --> 00:27:44,480
Xiaolian

533
00:27:45,119 --> 00:27:46,480
tu rostro y tus cejas...

534
00:27:46,799 --> 00:27:47,160
Esto...
Espera,

535
00:27:48,079 --> 00:27:49,000
La erupción no puede ser

